<br>
What is lvl requirement?<br>
Any special items needed for equipment?<br>
How often do you'll have guild events?<br>
What is expected as a guild mate?<br>
Is there a requirement of how much you play or how many events you attend?<br>
<br>
I think that is pretty much them. I appreciate everyone's time in answering them. I usually play often but lately having connection issues with cox cable so working on sk alt character since I get disconnected every 20 minutes or so. But when it gets worked out, I would like to maybe attend a couple of events as a guest to see how things work.<br>
<br>
Thanks<br>
